<P>
LONG BEACH WOMEN GET PAST FRESNO STATE, 104-98 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
FRESNO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Penny Moore scored 25 points and Trise Jackson added 22 as Cal State Long Beach 
outlasted Fresno State, 104-98, Thursday night in a Big West Conference women's 
basketball game. 
</P>
<P>
Simone Srubek scored 31 points in defeat for the Bulldogs (16-9, 9-6 in the Big 
West). Angelique Lee added 19 points and Vjera Kaludjerovich had 17 for the 
49ers (21-5, 13-2). 
</P>
