at the site of a methamphetamine lab in Lakeside. Below, a hollowed-out apple 
holding a packet of the drug was seized by U.S. marshals, along with numerous 
weapons and laboratory equipment. Photos by DAVE GATLEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
