</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022390-0082 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 180334 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1990, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 20; Column 4; National Desk 
</P>
