<P>
POLICE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT; POLICE 
-- LOS ANGELES; EMPLOYEE THEFT; ROBBERIES -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; DRUG 
TRAFFICKING -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; POLICE MISCONDUCT; QUALITY OF LIFE; 
