<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022390-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 180414 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 23, 1990, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
